%N A394930 Number of graphs with n vertices that have no induced regular subgraph of order 7.
%C A394930 The sequence eventually becomes zero. It is known that a(47)>0, but it is not known whether a(48)=0.
%H A394930 Paul W. Dyson and Brendan D. McKay, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2604.08215">Ramsey numbers for regular induced subgraphs</a>, arXiv:2604.08215 [math.CO] (2026).
