%H A394930 S. Fajtlowicz, T. McColgan, T. Read, and W. Staton, <a href="https://combinatorialpress.com/ars-articles/volume-039-ars-articles/ramsey-numbers-for-induced-regular-subgraphs/">Ramsey numbers for induced regular subgraphs</a>, Ars Combinatoria, 39 (1995) 149-154.
%Y A394930 Cf. A394573 (subgraphs of order 4), A394539 (order 5), A394462 (order 6), A394933 (order 7 or greater).
